g%20my%20quest%2C%20I'd%20unearthed%20treasures.%20There%20were%20photos%20of%20my%20grandpa%20I'd%20never%20seen%20alongside%20military%20documents%20displaying%20his%20signature.%20I%20calculated%20his%20age%20at%20every%20turn%2C%20finding%20context%20for%20family%20stories%20and%20drawing%20comparisons%20with%20my%20life.%20Years%20earlier%2C%20I'd%20sorted%20through%20a%20box%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdads-financial-love-letter-gives-peace-of-mind-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esweet%20love%20letters%3C%2Fa%3E%20exchanged%20between%20Grandpa%20Louie%20and%20my%20grandmother%20while%20he%20served%20overseas.%20These%20felt%20like%20a%20nice%20introduction%20to%20Grandpa.%20Genealogy%20brought%20me%20even%20closer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20dove%20into%20my%20grandpa's%20younger%20years%20by%20perusing%20newspapers%20from%20his%20tiny%20hometown%2C%20feeling%20giddy%20when%20I'd%20find%20mention%20of%20him%20or%20his%20loved%20ones.%20The%20marvelous%20mundanity%20captured%20my%20imagination%3A%20There%20were%20descriptions%20of%20egg%20deliveries%20and%20farm%20trades%20for%20%26quot%3Bfine%20hogs%26quot%3B%20among%20my%20great-great%20uncles.%20A%20frequent%20theme%20in%20the%20paper%20was%20reporting%20on%20the%20latest%20injuries%20and%20ailments%20afflicting%20my%20great-grandmother%2C%20Louie's%20mother.%20And%20perhaps%20most%20adorably%2C%20I%20stumbled%20upon%20a%20published%20letter%20to%20Santa%20Claus%20written%20by%20Grandpa%20himself%20at%20seven%20years%20old.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269d190fb-cbcb-44d8-8080-2418f90556c0%5C%22%3EI%20felt%20closer%20to%20him%20the%20more%20I%20found%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20deeper%20I%20dug%2C%20the%20closer%20I%20felt%20to%20this%20man%20who%20is%20such%20a%20part%20of%20me%20but%20whom%20I've%20never%20looked%20in%20the%20eye.%20Through%20photos%2C%20documents%2C%20and%20newspaper%20clippings%20%E2%80%94%20some%20of%20which%20had%20never%20been%20seen%20by%20my%20dad%20or%20his%20siblings%20%E2%80%94%20I%20felt%20like%20Grandpa%20Louie%2C%20and%20I%20were%20working%20on%20a%20secret%20project%20together%20as%20if%20he'd%20left%20me%20clues%20to%20unearth%20throughout%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20more%20incredibly%2C%20I%20tracked%20Grandpa's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fancestry-new-dna-tests-how-they-compare-2019-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ematernal%20line%20back%20to%20Ireland%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20my%20third%20great-grandmother%2C%20Sabina%2C%20who%20left%20Achill%20Island%20during%20the%20potato%20famine.%20Only%2022%20years%20old%2C%20she%20made%20the%20dangerous%20journey%20to%20Canada%20by%20boat%20and%20migrated%20to%20the%20Midwestern%20United%20States%2C%20where%20she%20settled%2C%20married%2C%20and%20continued%20the%20family%20line%20that%20allowed%20me%20to%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EObituaries%20discovered%20during%20my%20genealogy%20journey%20included%20locals'%20accounts%20of%20Sabina's%20warm%20demeanor%2C%20hardworking%20nature%2C%20and%20penchant%20for%20sharing%20stories%20of%20her%20life%20in%20Ireland.%20Because%20she%20lived%20into%20her%2090s%2C%20I%20was%20lucky%20enough%20to%20find%20two%20photos%20of%20Sabina%20%E2%80%94%20such%20treasures%20and%20unexpected%20bonuses%20in%20my%20quest.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20I%20continued%20to%20trace%20Grandpa%20Louie's%20life%20through%20the%20birth%20of%20his%2010%20children%20and%20his%20proud%20career%20as%20a%20truck%20driver%2C%20I%20inevitably%20arrived%20in%201987%2C%20the%20year%20he%20died%20of%20complications%20from%20leukemia.%20There%20were%20obituaries%20listing%20the%20basics%20of%20his%20life%20and%20death%2C%20yes%2C%20but%20there%20were%20also%20newspaper%20articles%20paying%20homage%20to%20his%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20piece%20in%20the%20Flint%20Journal%20described%20him%20as%20calm%20and%20good-humored%2C%20even%20quoting%20a%20few%20of%20Grandpa's%20jokes.%20I%20don't%20know%20what%20his%20voice%20sounded%20like%2C%20but%20reading%20his%20words%20is%20a%20gift.%20Other%20pieces%20posthumously%20lauded%20his%20dedication%20to%20union%20work%2C%20describing%20him%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Binstitution.%26quot%3B%20I%20didn't%20know%20feeling%20such%20pride%20for%20someone%20you'd%20never%20met%20was%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22cce74da2-6b3b-43d2-93a1-6bc982b7cd26%5C%22%3EIt%20didn't%20bring%20him%20back%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20dive%20into%20the%20world%20of%20amateur%20genealogy%20has%20not%20brought%20my%20grandfather%20back%2C%20nor%20has%20it%20fully%20eased%20the%20pervasive%20sadness%20I%20feel%20that%20our%20paths%20never%20crossed.%20But%20it%20has%20given%20me%20the%20gift%20of%20knowledge%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20connect%20with%20my%20grandfather%20as%20every%20version%20of%20himself%E2%80%94from%20the%20little%20boy%20writing%20letters%20to%20Santa%20Claus%20to%20the%20young%20military%20man%20to%20the%20driver%20and%20dad%20with%20a%20larger-than-life%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20peace%20in%20knowing%20that%20the%20seemingly%20mundane%20things%20we%20leave%20behind%20might%20matter%20to%20those%20who%20come%20after%20us.%20The%20documents%20we%20sign%2C%20the%20photos%20we%20pose%20for%2C%20the%20quick%20quotes%20we%20share%20with%20local%20reporters%2C%20the%20yearbooks%2C%20and%20the%20letters.%20These%20small%20slices%20of%20personal%20history%20create%20a%20portal%20between%20us%20and%20our%20family%20members.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20will%20always%20be%20true%20that%20I%20never%20met%20my%20Grandpa%20Louie.%20No%20amount%20of%20research%2C%20photographs%2C%20or%20glowing%20articles%20can%20change%20that.%20But%20I%20take%20comfort%20in%20knowing%20that%20so%20many%20pieces%20of%20him%20are%20still%20here%2C%20very%20much%20alive%2C%20tucked%20safely%20into%20my%20folders%20of%20genealogical%20finds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsid