%3EWhen%20they%20were%208%20and%20honing%20their%20reading%20skills%2C%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmultigenerational-family-cruise-vacation-kids-grandmother-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowed%20our%20kids%20to%20lead%20us%20around%20the%20ship%3C%2Fa%3E%20instead%20of%20the%20other%20way%20around.%20Most%20cruise%20ships%20have%20prominent%20signs%20to%20tell%20passengers%20what%20deck%20various%20activities%20are%20located%20on%2C%20making%20it%20easier%20to%20find%20your%20way%20around.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20heading%20to%20dinner%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcheap-way-get-ocean-view-cruise-disney-secret-porthole-room-tour-2023%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eon%20board%20the%20Disney%20Wonder%3C%2Fa%3E.%20As%20we%20approached%20the%20elevator%2C%20my%20partner%20pointed%20to%20the%20sign%20and%20asked%20our%20boys%2C%20%26quot%3BHow%20do%20we%20get%20to%20the%20Animator's%20Palate%20from%20here%3F%26quot%3B%20My%20kids%20carefully%20read%20the%20sign%20and%20saw%20that%20the%20restaurant%20was%20on%20Deck%204%20Aft.%20Based%20on%20that%20information%2C%20they%20learned%20that%20we%20had%20to%20use%20the%20elevator%20to%20go%20down%20four%20decks%20and%20that%20the%20restaurant%20was%20located%20at%20the%20back%20of%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22720%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Family%20posing%20for%20photo%20by%20cruise%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca0c10585f1dff88b1698c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20and%20her%20husband%20started%20giving%20their%20kids%20independence%20on%20cruises%20when%20they%20were%2010.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20took%20a%20little%20coaching%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fim-teaching-my-kids-to-embrace-imperfection-2023-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowing%20them%20to%20make%20mistakes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20by%20the%20time%20they%20were%2010%2C%20my%20kids%20were%20confidently%20navigating%20their%20way%20around%20cruise%20ships.%20We%20allowed%20them%20to%20leave%20the%20dinner%20table%20when%20they%20were%20done%20eating%2C%20make%20their%20way%20to%20the%20kid's%20club%2C%20and%20sign%20themselves%20in%2C%20letting%20my%20partner%20and%20I%20relax%20and%20enjoy%20each%20other's%20company.%20My%20kids%20would%20wolf%20down%20their%20mac%20and%20cheese%20and%20dash%20off%20to%20play%20games%20with%20the%20kids%20they%20met%20on%20board%2C%20and%20the%20grownups%20get%20to%20linger%20over%20dessert.%20Everybody%20was%20happy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20boys%20turned%2012%2C%20we%20lifted%20most%20restrictions%20and%20allowed%20them%20to%20roam%20freely%20on%20the%20cruise%20ship%2C%20with%20ever-loosening%20rules%20as%20they%20got%20older.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22053a2437-f9d0-483f-b176-a494243cc481%5C%22%3EYes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20have%20rules%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20boys%20are%2014%20and%2015.%20Don't%20let%20your%20mind%20leap%20to%20worst-case%20scenarios%20and%20visions%20of%20teens%20gone%20wild%20%E2%80%94%20grubby-handed%20kids%20cutting%20in%20line%20at%20the%20buffet%2C%20being%20loud%20during%20the%20shows%2C%20and%20running%20amuck%20on%20deck.%20While%20it%20sounds%20like%20a%20clich%C3%A9%2C%20oblivious%20mom%20response%2C%20my%20kids%20aren't%20like%20that.%20I%20have%20zero%20concerns%20about%20them%20doing%20something%20reckless%2C%20like%20trying%20to%20climb%20from%20one%20balcony%20to%20another%2C%20which%20is%20highly%20dangerous.%20They've%20earned%20their%20freedoms%20by%20behaving%20responsibly.%20And%20yes%2C%20of%20course%2C%20we%20have%20rules.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20require%20our%20kids%20to%20stay%20in%20contact%20with%20us%20via%20the%20chat%20function%20in%20the%20cruise%20line%20app%20throughout%20the%20cruise.%20No%20one%20is%20allowed%20in%20our%20stateroom%2C%20our%20kids%20cannot%20go%20in%20anyone%20else's%2C%20and%20we%20all%20get%20off%20and%20on%20the%20ship%20together.%20They're%20old%20enough%20to%20find%20food%20for%20themselves%2C%20but%20we%20insist%20on%20having%20dinner%20every%20night%20as%20a%20family.%20We%20communicate%20when%20planning%20our%20cruise%20so%20our%20kids%20have%20input%20and%20knowledge%20of%20what%20we'll%20do%20as%20a%20family%2C%20and%20when%20they%20get%20free%20time%2C%20we%20reinforce%20that%20on%20the%20first%20day%2C%20as%20soon%20as%20we%20get%20on%20the%20ship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22fcd84c42-2414-4f12-b842-081c9cda8462%5C%22%3EA%20sense%20of%20ownership%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20approach%20gives%20our%20kids%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20over%20their%20vacation%2C%20which%20helps%20them%20enjoy%20it%20more.%20Although%20I%20like%20to%20think%20of%20myself%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bcool-not-a-regular%26quot%3B%20mom%20whose%20kids%20want%20to%20hang%20out%20with%20me%20on%20vacation%2C%20if%20I'm%20honest%20with%20myself%2C%20they%20enjoy%20me%20more%20in%20smaller%20doses%20as%20hanging%20out%20with%20their%20peers%20becomes%20increasingly%20important.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20my%20teens%20commandeer%20unfamiliar%20territory%20using%20their%20wits%20and%20available%20resources%20is%20a%20proud%20mom%20moment%2C%20although%20it%20comes%20with%20a%20side%20of%20bittersweet%20to%20realize%20they%20need%20me%20less%20and%20less.%20Although%20figuring%20out%20basic%20shipboard%20geography%2C%20like%20being%20able%20to%20distinguish%20the%20port%20side%20from%20starboard%2C%20aren't%20skills%20they're%20likely%20to%20need%20in%20their%20everyday%20landlocked%20life%2C%20I%20see%20my%20kids%20making%20their%20way%20through%20all%20kinds%20of%20unfamiliar%20situations%20with%20a%20self-assuredness%20that%20started%20with%20a%20random%20decision%20to%20let%20them%20find%20their%20way%20to%20a%20shipboard%20restaurant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERe