n-profit%20Signal%20Technology%20Foundation%20that%20runs%20the%20end-to-end%20encrypted%20Signal%20app%20known%20for%20its%20digital%20security.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20AI%20agent%20is%20marketed%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bmagic%20genie%20bot%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20think%20multiple%20steps%20ahead%20and%20complete%20tasks%20for%20users%20so%20that%20%26quot%3Byour%20brain%20can%20sit%20in%20a%20jar%2C%20and%20you're%20not%20doing%20any%20of%20that%20yourself%2C%26quot%3B%20Whittaker%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20an%20example%2C%20she%20said%20agentic%20AI%20could%20accomplish%20tasks%20like%20finding%20a%20concert%2C%20booking%20tickets%2C%20and%20opening%20an%20app%20like%20Signal%20to%20message%20friends%20with%20concert%20ticket%20details.%20But%20at%20every%20step%20in%20that%20process%2C%20the%20AI%20agent%20would%20access%20data%20that%20the%20user%20may%20want%20to%20keep%20private%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20need%20access%20to%20our%20browser%2C%20an%20ability%20to%20drive%20that.%20It%20would%20need%20our%20credit%20card%20information%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20tickets.%20It%20would%20need%20access%20to%20our%20calendar%2C%20everything%20we're%20doing%2C%20everyone%20we're%20meeting.%20It%20would%20need%20access%20to%20Signal%20to%20open%20and%20send%20that%20message%20to%20our%20friends%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20would%20need%20to%20be%20able%20to%20drive%20that%20across%20our%20entire%20system%20with%20something%20that%20looks%20like%20root%20permission%2C%20accessing%20every%20single%20one%20of%20those%20databases%2C%20probably%20in%20the%20clear%20because%20there's%20no%20model%20to%20do%20that%20encrypted.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhittaker%20added%20that%20an%20AI%20agent%20powerful%20enough%20to%20do%20that%20would%20%26quot%3Balmost%20certainly%26quot%3B%20process%20data%20off-device%20by%20sending%20it%20to%20a%20cloud%20server%20and%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20there's%20a%20profound%20issue%20with%