Churachandpur%2C%20however%2C%20reached%20without%20any%20incident%20and%20faced%20no%20road%20blockade%2C%20officials%20said.%20The%20buses%20crossed%20the%20Meitei-dominant%20Bishnupur%20and%20reached%20Churachandpur's%20Kangvai%2C%20some%2055%20km%20from%20Imphal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConflict%20For%20Nearly%20Two%20Years%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20valley-dominant%20Meitei%20community%20and%20over%20a%20dozen%20distinct%20tribes%20collectively%20known%20as%20Kuki%2C%20who%20are%20dominant%20in%20some%20hill%20areas%20of%20Manipur%2C%20have%20been%20fighting%20since%20May%202023%20over%20a%20range%20of%20issues%20such%20as%20land%20rights%20and%20political%20representation.%20Over%20250%20have%20died%20in%20the%20violence%20and%20nearly%2050%2C000%20have%20been%20internally%20displaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fo7efg6h8_manipur-protest_625x300_08_March_25.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKuki%20leaders%2C%20nearly%20two%20dozen%20militant%20groups%20that%20have%20signed%20the%20suspension%20of%20operations%20(SoO)%20agreement%2C%20and%20their%20frontal%20civil%20organisations%20have%20demanded%20the%20Centre%20give%20them%20a%20separate%20administration%20before%20allowing%20communities%20to%20move%20freely%20across%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeitei%20organisations%20have%20questioned%20why%20thousands%20of%20internally%20displaced%20people%20living%20in%20relief%20camps%20are%20threatened%20by%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20from%20returning%20home%20to%20rebuild%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20why%20people%20cannot%20travel%20safely%20on%20national%20highways%2C%20when%20talks%20can%20go%20on%20simultaneously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Meitei%20Heritage%20Society%20in%20a%20statement%20said%20%26quot%3Bthe%20blockade%20of%20the%20National%20Highway%20in%20Kangpokpi%20by%20Chin%20Kuki%20protesters%20and%20their%20armed%20groups%20is%20a%20deeply%20disturbing%20and%20a%20deliberate%20act%20of%20defiance%2C%20which%20directly%20challenges%20the%20decision%20of%20the%20Union%20Home%20Ministry%20to%20reopen%20the%20highways%2C%20a%20step%20taken%20towards%20restoring%20peace%20and%20normalcy%20in%20Manipur.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20should%20not%20succumb%20to%20the%20handful%20of%20militants%20and%20groups%20propped%20up%20by%20them%20and%20demonstrate%20that%20those%20challenging%20the%20sovereignty%20of%20the%20Indian%20state%20and%20rule%20of%20law%20will%20face%20exemplary%20action%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Meitei%20civil%20society%20organisation%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fd386rkcg_manipur-protest_625x300_08_March_25.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatureCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Kuki-Zo%20groups%20pointed%20at%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20that%20began%20in%20May%202023%20as%20the%20reason%20why%20they%20escalated%20their%20demand%20from%20an%20autonomous%20council%20to%20a%20separate%20administration%2C%20or%20a%20Union%20Territory%20with%20an%20assembly%2C%20Meitei%20leaders%20have%20pointed%20at%20decades-old%20evidence%20of%20Kuki%20groups%20working%20to%20form%20'Kukiland'%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20World%20Kuki-Zo%20Intellectual%20Council%20(WKZIC)%20in%20a%20memorandum%20to%20Manipur's%20new%20Governor%20on%20January%2015%20said%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20have%20been%20demanding%20a%20state%20%26quot%3Bsince%201946-47.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20years%20before%20May%202023%2C%20Kuki%20protests%2C%20gatherings%20and%20academic%20discussions%20have%20mentioned%20the%20demand%20for%20a%20separate%20area%20carved%20out%20of%20Manipur.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741459680000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2F7gu39dt_manipur-protest_625x300_08_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F1-killed-in-clashes-claim-kuki-groups-announce-shutdown-in-parts-of-manipur-7879400%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20protester%20from%20the%20Kuki%20tribes%20was%20killed%20in%20clashes%20with%20the%20security%20forces%20in%20Manipur%20today%20as%20buses%20moved%20out%20of%20the%20state%20capital%20Imphal%20towards%20other%20districts%2C%20following%20the%20Centre's%20order%20to%20ensure%20free%20movement%20across%20the%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20issues%20'do%20not%20travel'%20advisory%20for%20India-Pakistan%20border%2C%20citing%20'terrorism'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741459454000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118809493%2Cimgsize-511320.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fterrorism-and-armed-conflict-us-issues-do-not-travel-advisory-for-india-pakistan-border-key-pak-regions%2Farticleshow%2F118809493.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20US%20State%20Department%20issued%20a%20travel%20advisory%20warning%20against%20travel%20to%20areas%20near%20the%20India-Pakistan%20border%2C%20the%20Line%20of%20Control%2C%20and%20the%20provinces%20of%20Balochistan%20and%20Khyber%20Pakhtunkhwa%20due%20to%20terrorism%20and%20potential%20for%20armed%20conflict.%20Americans%20are%20specifically%20advised%20to%20avoid%20these%20regions%20because%20of%20frequent%20terrorist%20attacks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20WORLD%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Findia%2Fterrorism-and-armed-conflict-us-issues-do-not-t