Masala%20Ad%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20consumer%20disputes%20redressal%20commission%20in%20Jaipur%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Bollywood%20actors%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20Tiger%20Shroff%20over%20an%20allegedly%20misleading%20advertisement%20for%20a%20pan%20masala.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20District%20Consumer%20Disputes%20Redressal%20Commission%2C%20Jaipur%20II%2C%20also%20issued%20a%20similar%20notice%20to%20Vimal%20Kumar%20Agarwal%2C%20chairman%20of%20JB%20Industries%20that%20manufactures%20Vimal%20Pan%20Masala%2C%20and%20directed%20all%20parties%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20March%2019.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20hearing%20date%20has%20been%20fixed%20at%2010am.%20If%20you%20fail%20to%20appear%20in%20person%20or%20through%20your%20authorised%20representative%2C%20the%20complaint%20will%20be%20decided%20ex%20parte%20on%20the%20above%20mentioned%20hearing%20date%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20notice%2C%20issued%20by%20commission%20chairman%20Gyarsilal%20Meena%20and%20member%20Hemlata%20Agarwal%20in%20Hindi%20on%20March%205%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20commission%20also%20directed%20all%20the%20actors%20and%20the%20pan%20masala%20manufacturing%20company%20to%20file%20their%20responses%20within%2030%20days%20from%20the%20day%20of%20receipt%20of%20the%20notice.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20immediate%20comment%20from%20the%20actors%20or%20the%20company%20till%20the%20time%20of%20filing%20this%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20notice%20was%20issued%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20a%20complaint%20by%20Jaipur-based%20advocate%20Yogendra%20Singh%20Badiyal%2C%20who%20claimed%20the%20advertisement%20says%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Edaane%20daane%20mein%20hai%20kesar%20ka%20dum%3C%2Fem%3E%20(every%20grain%20of%20the%20said%20pan%20masala%20has%20the%20power%20of%20saffron)%26quot%3B.%20Due%20to%20this%2C%20%26quot%3Bapplicant%20number%20one%20(JB%20Industries)%20is%20making%20crores%20of%20rupees%20and%20the%20common%20people%20are%20regularly%20consuming%20the%20pan%20masala%20which%20is%20harmful%20for%20health%20and%20inviting%20serious%20diseases%20like%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2068-year-old%20lawyer%20said%20the%20public%20is%20being%20lured%20to%20purchase%20Vimal%20Pan%20Masala%20%26quot%3Bin%20the%20name%20of%20saffron-containing%20gutkha%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCommon%20people%20are%20getting%20confused%20in%20the%20name%20of%20saffron%20while%20there%20is%20no%20mixture%20of%20any%20substance%20like%20saffron%20in%20the%20said%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20price%20of%20saffron%20in%20the%20market%20is%20Rs%204%20lakh%20per%20kg%20and%20the%20pan%20masala%20costs%20only%20Rs%205%2C%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20saffron%20cannot%20be%20mixed%2C%20leave%20alone%20its%20fragrance%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Badiyal%20demanded%20action%20against%20the%20manufacturing%20firm%20and%20the%20actors%20involved%20in%20the%20product's%20promotion%20%26quot%3Bfor%20spreading%20false%20information%20and%20cheating%20the%20general%20public%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDue%20to%20this%20false%20publicity%20and%20propagation%2C%20general%20public%20is%20facing%20loss%20of%20life%20and%20health%2C%20for%20which%20the%20applicants%20are%20separately%20and%20indirectly%20responsible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20demanded%20a%20fine%20be%20imposed%20on%20the%20accused%2C%20and%20a%20ban%20on%20the%20advertisement%20as%20well%20as%20the%20pan%20masala%20%26quot%3Bwith%20immediate%20effect...%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20justice%20and%20the%20general%20public%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lawyer%20said%20he%20%26quot%3Bparticipates%20in%20social%20services%20and%20social%20awareness%20activities%20and%20takes%20action%20for%20the%20upliftment%20of%20the%20society%20and%20against%20social%20evils%20and%20propaganda%26quot%3B.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(With%20inputs%20from%20Sushant%20Pareek)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741458780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Favu3vu6o_shah-rukh-khan-pan-masala-ad_625x300_08_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshah-rukh-khan-ajay-devgn-tiger-shroff-get-notice-over-vimal-pan-masala-ad-saffron-jaipur-commission-7880154%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20consumer%20disputes%20redressal%20commission%20in%20Jaipur%20has%20issued%20a%20notice%20to%20Shah%20Rukh%20Khan%2C%20Ajay%20Devgn%20and%20Tiger%20Shroff%20over%20an%20allegedly%20misleading%20advertisement%20for%20Vimal%20Pan%20Masala.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Fresh%20Chinese%20tariffs%20on%20Canadian%20agricultural%20and%20food%20products%20open%20new%20front%20in%20brewing%20trade%20war%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Canadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20are%20pictured%20here%20in%202016.%20Their%20respective%20countries%20are%20imposing%20tariffs%20against%20each%20other.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cc23fd69253ccddf98b126%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECanadian%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20and%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping.%3Cp%3ELintao%20Zhang%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EChina%20announced%20on%20Saturday%20that%20it%20will%20impose%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20Canada%20from%20March%2020.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20tariffs%20will%20hit%20Canadian%20agricultural%20and%20food%20products%2C%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBeijing%20cited%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20Canadian%20levies%20on%20Chinese%20EVs%20as%20part%20of%20the%20reason%20behind%20the%20decision.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EChina%20has%20announced%20that%20it%20will%20impose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-retaliate-trump-trade-war-tariffs-soybeans-agriculture-two-sessions-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eretaliatory%20tariffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20certain%20Canadian%20agricultural%20and%20food%20products%20from%20March%2020%2C%20deepening%20concerns%20over%20a%20brewing%20global%20trade%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Saturday%2C%20China's%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20said%20a%20100%25%20tariff%20would%20be%20imposed%20on%20rapeseed%20oil%2C%20rapeseed%20meal%2C%20and%20pea%20imports%20from%20Canada%2C%20as%20well%20as%20a%2025%25%20tariff%20on%20some%20seafood%20products%20and%20pork.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20ministry%20said%20the%20decision%20was%20made%20in%20response%20to%20Canada's%20%26quot%3Bdiscriminatory%26quot%3B%20100%25%20levy%20on%20Chinese%20electric%20vehicles%20and%2025%25%20tariffs%20on%20Chinese%20steel%20and%20aluminum%2C%20which%20came%20into%20force%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerica's%20neighbor%20to%20the%20north%20is%20a%20major%20global%20producer%20of%20rapeseed%2C%20also%20known%20as%20canola%2C%20and%20China%20is%20its%20second-largest%20market%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Canola%20Council%20Of%20Canada.%20Canadian%20exports%20of%20canola%20seed%2C%20oil%2C%20and%20meal%20to%20China%20were%20valued%20at%20C%245%20billion%20(around%20%243.5%20billion)%20in%202023%2C%20per%20the%20Canola%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeijing's%20announcement%20means%20Canada%20is%20now%20facing%20a%20trade%20battle%20on%20two%20fronts%20as%20pressure%20on%20its%20economy%20continues%20to%20grow.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJosh%20Lipsky%2C%20the%20senior%20director%20of%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20GeoEconomics%20Center%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20timing%20of%20China's%20tariffs%20announcement%20was%20particularly%20noteworthy.%20The%20move%20came%20just%20a%20day%20before%20Canada's%20governing%20Liberal%20Party%20is%20set%20to%20announce%20a%20new%20leader%20after%20Prime%20Minister%20Justin%20Trudeau%20said%20in%20January%20that%20he%20would%20resign.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChina's%20needed%20to%20get%20the%20retaliation%20done%2C%26quot%3B%20Lipsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20it's%20China%20trying%20to%20reset%20with%20Canada%20ahead%20of%20what's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20much%20broader%20trade%20conflict%20with%20the%20US%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20continued%2C%20adding%20that%20Beijing%20likely%20wanted%20to%20%26quot%3Bclear%20the%20decks%26quot%3B%20before%20a%20new%20Canadian%20leader%20was%20in%20place.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20may%20also%20have%20been%20designed%20to%20serve%20as%20a%20warning%20to%20Canada%20not%20to%20align%20itself%20too%20closely%20with%20the%20US%20on%20trade%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F03%2F08%2Fbusiness%2Fchina-tariffs-canada.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E%20reported%20that%20China%20Central%20Television%20had%20released%20a%20commentary%20that%20called%20the%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Ba%20powerful%20countermeasure%20to%20Canada's%20wrong%20choice%2C%20and%20a%20strong%20warning%20to%20some%20countries%20that%20intend%20to%20impose%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20China%20in%20exchange%20for%20the%20United%20States%20not%20to%20impose%20additional%20tariffs%20on%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPaul%20Smetanin%2C%20president%20of%20the%20Canadian%20Centre%20for%20Economic%20Analysis%2C%20told%20BI%20that%20China's%20move%20was%20not%20surprising%20but%20that%20it%20underscored%20the%20%26quot%3Bdelicate%20environment%20in%20which%20Canada%20must%20manage%20its%20global%20economic%20interests.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoving%20forward%2C%20the%20government's%20priority%20must%20be%20to%20develop%20a%20nimble%20trade%20strateg