re%20values.%20So%20when%20he%20told%20me%20he%20had%20to%20move%20back%20to%20the%20UK%20because%20his%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-visa-moved-usa-canada-immigrants-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3ECanadian%20working%20holiday%20visa%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20was%20about%20to%20expire%2C%20I%20took%20a%20risk.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20was%20July%202018%2C%20and%20we%20turned%20into%20fast%20friends%20after%20becoming%20co-workers%20a%20few%20months%20prior.%20We%20went%20out%20for%20what%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%20a%20casual%20goodbye%20drink%2C%20but%20the%20night%20ended%20up%20lasting%2014%20hours%20as%20we%20chatted%2C%20laughed%2C%20sang%2C%20and%20hopped%20from%20venue%20to%20venue.%20By%20the%20end%2C%20we%20confessed%20that%20we%20both%20had%20feelings%20for%20each%20other.%20We%20knew%20things%20would%20be%20complicated%20with%20his%20flight%20only%20a%20few%20days%20away%2C%20but%20there%20was%20something%20there.%20By%20the%20time%20he%20landed%20in%20the%20UK%2C%20we%20had%20both%20texted%20that%20we%20wanted%20to%20take%20our%20chances%20on%20a%20romantic%20relationship.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22d6ff1207-9414-4150-96f3-64148d31e642%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ELong-distance%20didn't%20last%20long%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20were%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwoman-only-been-long-distance-relationships-whole-life-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Elong-distance%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%2010%20months%2C%20seeing%20each%20other%20only%20twice%20before%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20UK%20in%20May%202019.%20The%20distance%20was%20challenging%2C%20but%20it%20encouraged%20us%20to%20get%20creative%20to%20maintain%20our%20connection.%20We'd%20spend%20every%20moment%20we%20could%20messaging%20each%20other%20or%20coming%20up%20with%2