3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb3b2669253ccddf98a01d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump%20limits%20eligibility%20for%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program.%3Cp%3EAlex%20Wong%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20signed%20an%20executive%20order%20aimed%20at%20limiting%20eligibility%20for%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETrump%20said%20the%20order%20would%20restrict%20employers%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Banti-American%26quot%3B%20activities%20from%20participating.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMillions%20of%20government%20and%20nonprofit%20workers%20rely%20on%20PSLF%20for%20student-debt%20relief.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Donald%20Trump's%20latest%20executive%20order%20took%20on%20a%20major%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-forgiveness-pslf-borrowers-getting-debt-cancellation-biden-relief-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Estudent-loan%20forgiveness%20program%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20administration's%20latest%20attack%20on%20workers%20in%20government%20and%20nonprofits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Friday%2C%20Trump%20signed%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fpresidential-actions%2F2025%2F03%2Frestoring-public-service-loan-forgiveness%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eexecutive%20order%3C%2Fa%3E%20aimed%20at%20limiting%20eligibility%20for%20the%20Public%20Service%20Loan%20Forgiveness%20program%2C%20which%20forgives%20student%20debt%20for%20workers%20like%20teachers%2C%20healthcare%20workers%20and%20police%20officers%20after%2010%20years%20of%20qualifying%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20order's%20incendiary%20rhetoric%20said%20that%20organizations%20engaging%20in%20%26quot%3Bactivities%20that%20advance%20illegal%20immigration%2C%20terrorism%2C%20child%20abuse%2C%20discrimination%2C%20and%20public%20disruptions%26quot%3B%20would%20be%20barred%20from%20the%20loan%20forgiveness%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20PSLF%20Program%20also%20creates%20perverse%20incentives%20that%20can%20increase%20the%20cost%20of%20tuition%2C%20can%20load%20students%20in%20low-need%20majors%20with%20unsustainable%20debt%2C%20and%20may%20push%20students%20into%20organizations%20that%20hide%20under%20the%20umbrella%20of%20a%20non-profit%20designation%20and%20degrade%20our%20national%20interest%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20order%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20unclear%20what%20organizations%20the%20Trump%20administration%20intends%20to%20accuse%20of%20these%20%26quot%3Banti-American%26quot%3B%20activities.%20This%20comes%20as%20the%20administration%20carries%20out%20mass%20layoffs%20of%20federal%20workers.%20The%20order%20directed%20Linda%20McMahon%2C%20Trump's%20new%20education%20secretary%2C%20to%20redefine%20what%20%26quot%3Bpublic%20service%26quot%3B%20is%20to%20align%20with%20the%20administration's%20political%20views.%20Student-loan%20borrower%20advocates%20say%20they'll%20take%20the%20administration%20to%20court%20if%20they%20follow%20through%20on%20this%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20latest%20Education%20Department%20data%2C%20over%202%20million%20borrowers%20were%20enrolled%20in%20PSLF%20with%20eligible%20employers%20as%20of%20December%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20isn't%20the%20first%20time%20Trump%20has%20targeted%20PSLF.%20During%20his%20first%20term%2C%20his%20Department%20of%20Education%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-debt-cancellation-payment-pause-borrowers-disabilities-defrauded-2021-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eran%20up%20a%20backlog%20of%20PSLF%20applications%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20has%20also%20previously%20suggested%20eliminating%20the%20program%20altogether.%20Doing%20so%20would%20require%20an%20act%20of%20Congress%2C%20and%20there%20has%20yet%20to%20be%20sufficient%20support%20to%20eliminate%20the%20program.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20address%20the%20backlog%20of%20PSLF%20applications%20and%20paperwork%20issues%20with%20the%20program%2C%20former%20President%20Joe%20Biden's%20Education%20Department%20introduced%20a%20limited-time%20waiver%20to%20allow%20borrowers'%20past%20payments%20%E2%80%94%20including%20those%20previously%20deemed%20ineligible%20for%20PSLF%20%E2%80%94%20to%20count%20toward%20their%20forgiveness%20progress.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBiden%20also%20carried%20out%20targeted%20relief%20for%20PSLF%20borrowers%20under%20one-time%20account%20adjustments%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20bring%20payments%20up-to-date.%20In%20his%20final%20weeks%20in%20office%2C%20he%20announced%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstudent-loan-borrowers-debt-cancellation-biden-last-relief-before-trump-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%24465%20million%20in%20debt%20cancellation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%206%2C100%20borrowers%20enrolled%20in%20PSLF.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmid%20Trump's%20efforts%20to%20limit%20the%20program%2C%20McMahon%20said%20during%20her%20confirmation%20hearing%20that%20she%20would%20honor%20the%20program%20as%20Congress%20intended.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20added%3A%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20want%20stronger%20or%20more%20programs%20for%20loan%20forgiveness%2C%20then%20I%20think%20Congress%20should%20pass%20those%20programs%2C%20and%20then%20we%20would%20implement%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20advocacy%20groups%20criticized%20the%20executive%20order.%20Aaron%20Ament%2C%20president%20of%20borrower%20protection%20group%20Student%20Defense%2C%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20that%20PSLF%20was%20created%20by%20a%20%26quot%3Bbipartisan%20act%20of%20Congress%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BAmericans%20have%20worked%20hard%20and%20made%20life%20decisions%20under%20the%20assumption%20that%20the%20US%20keeps%20its%20word.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThreatening%20to%20punish%20hardworking%20Americans%20for%20their%20employers'%20perceived%20political%20views%20is%20about%20as%20flagrant%20a%20violation%20of%20the%20First%20Amendment%20as%20you%20can%20imagine%2C%26quot%3B%20Ament%20said.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20Trump%20Administration%20follows%20through%20on%20this%20threat%2C%20they%20can%20plan%20to%20see%20us%20in%20court.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aasheffey%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Easheffey%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Cem%3Eor%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3ESignal%20at%20asheffey.97.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-pslf-education-department-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741453041000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67cb3b3669253ccddf98a025%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-pslf-education-department-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22President%20Trump's%20order%20aims%20to%20disqualify%20employers%20engaging%20in%20what%20he%20labeled%20%26quot%3Banti-American%26quot%3B%20activities%20from%20student%20loan%20forgiveness.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22asheffey%40businessinsider.com%20(Ayelet%20Sheffey)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A561%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-limits-public-service-loan-forgiveness-program-psl