nd.%3Cp%3EScott%20Olson%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-ceo-said-mobile-ordering-chipped-away-at-brands-soul-2025-2%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks%3C%2Fa%3E%20booked%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20profit%20in%20a%20Swiss%20subsidiary%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20a%20new%20report%20says.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20move%20appeared%20to%20reduce%20Starbucks'%20tax%20bill%20in%20other%20countries.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt's%20the%20latest%20example%20of%20companies%20using%20tax%20havens%20to%20avoid%20tax%20rates%20in%20the%20US%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EA%20little-known%20Starbucks%20subsidiary%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoving-us-to-switzerland-better-quality-of-life-staying-abroad-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESwitzerland%3C%2Fa%3E%20appears%20to%20have%20played%20a%20big%20role%20in%20how%20much%20the%20coffee%20chain%20paid%20over%20the%20last%20decade%20in%20taxes%2C%20according%20to%20a%20new%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20paper%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchanges-coming-to-starbucks-sales-free-refills-fewer-app-rewards-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks%20Coffee%3C%2Fa%3E%20Trading%20Company%2C%20or%20SCTC%2C%20based%20in%20the%20Swiss%20Canton%20of%20Vaud%2C%20is%20responsible%20for%20sourcing%20unroasted%20coffee%20from%20countries%20like%20Colombia%20and%20Rwanda%20before%20it's%20used%20in%20beverages%20at%20Starbucks'%20caf%C3%A9s.%20It%20also%20oversees%20Starbucks'%20Coffee%20and%20Farmer%20Equity%20Practices%20program%20for%20ethical%20coffee%20sourcing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20released%20Saturday%20by%20the%20Centre%20for%20International%20Corporate%20Tax%20Accountability%20and%20Research%2C%20or%20CICTAR%2C%20there's%20also%20evidence%20that%20since%202015%2C%20the%20subsidiary%20has%20helped%20shift%20about%20%241.3%20billion%20in%20Starbucks%20profits%20away%20from%20other%20countries%20where%20they%20would%20have%20been%20subject%20to%20higher%20tax%20rates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20chain%20is%20hardly%20the%20only%20major%20company%20that%20books%20profits%20outside%20the%20United%20States%2C%20and%20the%20report's%20authors%20found%20no%20evidence%20that%20the%20company%20was%20doing%20anything%20illegal.%20But%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-howard-schultz-ceo-gen-z-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStarbucks'%20reputation%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20being%20conscious%20of%20its%20role%20in%20society%20contrasts%20with%20its%20use%20of%20tax%20loopholes%2C%20said%20Jason%20Ward%2C%20principal%20analyst%20at%20Australia-based%20CICTAR.%20%3Cspan%3EThe%20group%20is%20funded%20by%20trade%20unions%20as%20well%20as%20trusts%20and%20foundations.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarbucks%20is%20different%20in%20that%20it%20really%20does%20bank%20on%20its%20image%20of%20social%20responsibility%2C%26quot%3B%20Ward%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20uses%20Switzerland-based%20SCTC%20to%20book%20the%20cost%20of%20the%20unroasted%20coffee%20beans%2C%20even%20though%20the%20beans%20don't%20appear%20to%20move%20through%20Switzerland%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESCTC%20%26quot%3Bthen%20sells%20the%20exact%20same%20green%20coffee%20beans%20at%20a%20higher%20price%20to%20other%20entities%20in%20the%20Starbucks%20corporate%20structure%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%20That%20markup%20was%20about%203%25%20between%202005%20and%202010%2C%20then%20rose%20to%2018%25%20between%202011%20and%202014%2C%20CICTAR's%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECICTAR%20could%20not%20find%20%26quot%3Bany%20significant%20change%20in%20business%20practices%20or%20underlying%20costs%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20justify%20the%20jump%20in%20profits%2C%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20not%20like%20they're%20roasting%20coffee%20or%20researching%20the%20different%20types%20of%20beans%20or%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Ward%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere's%20nothing%20like%20that%20going%20on%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Switzerland%2C%20profits%20from%20those%20markups%20are%20taxed%20at%20%26quot%3Ba%20significantly%20lower%20tax%20rate%26quot%3B%20than%20if%20they%20had%20been%20booked%20in%20the%20United%20States%20or%20other%20countries%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20exact%20tax%20rate%20that%20Starbucks%20pays%20in%20Switzerland%20isn't%20publicly%20known%2C%20US%20companies%20paid%20an%20average%20rate%20of%203.9%25%20in%20the%20country%2C%20according%20to%20an%20analysis%20of%20IRS%20data%20by%20the%20Institute%20on%20Taxation%20and%20Economic%20Policy%2C%20or%20ITEP.%20The%20US%20corporate%20tax%20rate%20is%2021%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20between%202015%20and%202021%2C%20SCTC%20has%20paid%20between%20%24125%20million%20and%20%24150%20million%20in%20dividends%20annually%20to%20another%20Starbucks%20subsidiary%2C%20Netherlands-based%20Starbucks%20Coffee%20EMEA%20B.V.%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report.%20These%20payments%20do%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20taxed%20either%20upon%20leaving%20Switzerland%20or%20upon%20entering%20the%20Netherlands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20looked%20at%20financial%20filings%20for%20Starbucks%20subsidiaries%20around%20Europe%20to%20trace%20profits%20booked%20at%20SCTC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20response%20that%20CICTAR%20included%20on%20page%204%20of%20the%20report%2C%20a%20Starbucks%20spokesperson%20said%20that%20the%20report's%20claims%20%26quot%3Bfail%20to%20accurately%20reflect%20our%20business%20model%20and%20how%20different%20parts%20of%20our%20business%20contribute%20to%20the%20company's%20success.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStarbucks%20pays%20appropriate%20and%20correct%20levels%20of%20tax%20in%20all%20jurisdictions%20in%20which%20it%20operates%20and%20proactively%20works%20with%20tax%20authorities%20to%20inform%20them%20of%20its%20business%20model%20and%20related%20tax%20implications%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Starbucks%20spokesperson%20told%20BI%20that%20the%20company%20%26quot%3Bis%20in%20full%20compliance%20with%20tax%20laws%20around%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20and%20had%20an%20effective%20global%20tax%20rate%20of%20about%2024%25%20last%20year.%20SCTC%20provides%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3Ehigh-quality%20coffee%20to%20meet%20our%20global%20demand%26quot%3B%20and%20includes%20farmer%20support%20centers%20in%20coffee-growing%20areas%20of%20the%20world.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSwitzerland%20has%20been%20a%20global%20hub%20for%20coffee%20trading%20for%20decades%20and%20SCTC%20is%20based%20there%20to%20help%20us%20access%20the%20world's%20best%20coffee%20trading%20talent%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20spokesperson%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStarbucks%20isn't%20the%20only%20company%20that%20looks%20abroad%20to%20minimize%20its%20tax%20obligations.%20A%202021%20report%20from%20CICTAR%20looked%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-tax-avoidance-50-dutch-shell-companies-5-billion-revenue-2021-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUber's%20use%20of%20shell%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20Netherlands%20to%20limit%20its%20tax%20bill%2C%20for%20instance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20companies%20and%20wealthy%20individuals%20store%20money%20in%20a%20variety%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftax-havens-for-millionaires-around-the-world-2019-11%23%3A~%3Atext%3DTax%2520havens%2520are%2520places%2520where%2520business%2520people%2520and%2520other%2520super%2Clocations%252C%2520like%2520the%2520Caribbean%2520islands.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etax-haven%3C%2Fa%3E%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20the%20Cayman%20Islands%2C%20since%20they%20charge%20less%20in%20taxes%20than%20their%20home%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20or%20none%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECICTAR's%20findings%20on%20Starbucks%20aren't%20surprising%2C%20said%20Matthew%20Gardner%2C%20senior%20fellow%20at%20ITEP.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20thing%20that%20every%20company%20or%20every%20industry%2C%20companies%20in%20every%20industry%20that%20have%20lots%20of%20intangible%20assets%20are%20doing%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20storing%20profits%20in%20tax%20havens%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20US%20government's%20responses%20to%20the%20strategy%20%E2%80%94%20goes%20back%20decades%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202004%20tax%20holiday%2C%20for%20example%2C%20allowed%20corporations%20to%20bring%20profits%20to%20the%20United%20States%20from%20overseas%20at%20a%20much-reduced%20tax%20rate.%20The%20Tax%20Cuts%20and%20Jobs%20Act%20of%202017%2C%20passed%20during%20President%20Donald%20Trump's%20first%20term%2C%20also%20contained%20provisions%20to%20bring%20more%20corporate%20profits%20back%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20many%20companies%20have%20continued%20using%20offshore%20tax%20havens%2C%20Gardner%20said.%20An%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fitep.org%2Foffshore-tax-havens-corporate-tax-avoidance-demonstrates-need-for-global-minimum-tax%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EITEP%20analysis%20of%20IRS%20data%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%202020%20found%20that%20American-owned%20companies%20reported%20%24390%20billion%20in%20profits%20across%2015%20likely%20tax%20havens%2C%20including%20the%20Cayman%20Islands%2C%20Ireland%2C%20and%20Switzerland.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELarge%20companies'%20tax%20avoidance%20ultimately%20increases%20the%20tax%20burden%20on%20other%20taxpayers%2C%20including%20individuals%20and%20small%20businesses%2C%20Gardner%20said.%20It%20can%20also%20lead%20governments%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffederal-agencies-musk-doge-targeted-list-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eslash%20spending%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20cut%20programs%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20way%20in%20which%20the%20revenue%20loss%20from%20these%20offshore%20profits%20can%20be%20paid%20for%20hurts%20the%20rest%20of%20us%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aabitter%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eabitter%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20808-854-4501.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-used-a-swiss-subsidiary-to-avoid-taxes-report-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741448538000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67ca1a3d69253ccddf9888c7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-used-a-swiss-subsidiary-to-avoid-taxes-report-2025-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Starbucks%20booked%20millions%20in%20profit%20at%20a%20Swiss%20subsidiary%2C%20where%20the%20company%20likely%20paid%20less%20in%20taxes%20than%20it%20would%20have%20elsewhere%2C%20a%20report%20found.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abitter%40businessinsider.com%20(Alex%20Bitter)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A289%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-used-a-swiss-subsidiary-to-avoid-taxes-report-2025-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%2