y%20clear%2C%20the%20present%20military%20to%20military%20relationship%20is%20very%20strong.%20And%2C%20we%20exchanging%20note%20on%20regular%20basis%2C%20to%20avoid%20any%20kind%20of%20a%20misgiving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20was%20also%20asked%20how%20the%20Indian%20Army%20looked%20at%20the%20Pakistan-China%20equation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20we%20have%20to%20understand%20is%20that...%20we%20have%20to%20be%20very%20clear%20that%20there%20is%20a%20high%20degree%20of%20collusivity%2C%20which%20we%20must%20accept.%20In%20terms%20of%20the%20virtual%20field%2C%20it's%20nearly%20100%20per%20cent%3B%20in%20terms%20of%20physical%2C%20I%20would%20say%20most%20of%20the%20equipment%20there%20is%20of%20Chinese%20origin%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Army%20chief%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20this%20is%20the%20situation%20as%20of%20today%2C%20as%20far%20as%20collusivity%20is%20concerned.%20What%20it%20means%2C%20as%20far%20as%20I%20am%20concerned%2C%20the%20two-front%20threat%20...%20is%20a%20reality%20for%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20January%202021%2C%20the%20then%20Army%20chief%20Gen%20M%20M%20Naravane%20too%20said%20that%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20Pakistan%20and%20China%2C%20%26quot%3Bthe%20threat%20of%20collusivity%20cannot%20be%20wished%20away.%26quot%3B%20General%20Dwivedi%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20situation%20along%20the%20LAC%20in%20eastern%20Ladakh%20since%20the%20Special%20Representative-level%20(SR-level)%20meeting%20in%20December%202024%2C%20following%20an%20agreement%20that%20was%20finalised%20between%20the%20two%20countries%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Assassin's%20Mace%20has%20lived%20through%20its%20life.%20It%20may%20not%20be%20more%20relevant%20today.%20And%2C%20if%20you%20see%2C%20as%20far%20as%20the%20terrain%20of%20the%20Himalayas%20is%20concerned%2C%20the%20terrain%20plays%20a%20very%20favourable%20role%20as%20far%20as%20India%20is%20concerned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20second%20issue%20is%2C%20you%20may%20have%20superiority%20in%20anything%2C%20but%20what%20is%20important%20is%20at%20the%20point%20of%20application%2C%20are%20you%20able%20to%20amass%20that%20kind%20of%20resource%20application%2C%20strength%20and%20the%20impact%20which%20is%20required%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20that%20way%2C%20Indian%20Army%20is%20adequately%20poised%20to%20take%20care%20of%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Army%20chief%2C%20however%2C%20called%20for%20%26quot%3Bcoexistence%2C%20cooperation%20and%20coordination%26quot%3B%20to%20opine%20it%20was%20not%20good%20for%20the%20countries%20to%20engage%20in%20a%20war.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20the%20war%20in%20interest%20of%20both%20the%20countries%3F%20the%20answer%20is%20no.%20So%2C%20what%20we%20are%20looking%20at%20is%2C%20how%20can%20we%20harmonise...%20the%20situation%20as%20of%20today%2C%20and%20manage%20it%20till%20the%20diplomatic%20situation%20come%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20Working%20Mechanism%20for%20Consultation%20%26amp%3B%20Coordination%20on%20India-China%20Border%20Affairs%20(WMCC)%20and%20SRs%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20December.%20After%20that%2C%20the%20foreign%20secretary%20again%20went%20to%20China%20to%20witness%20a%20%26quot%3Blot%20of%20positive%20signalling%26quot%3B%20from%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20WMCC%20meeting%20should%20be%20taking%20place%20soon%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20query%20on%20the%20Depsang%20and%20Demchok%20areas%2C%20the%20general%20said%20the%20second%20and%20third%20rounds%20of%20patrolling%20have%20taken%20place%2C%20and%20both%20sides%20are%20cooperating%20with%20each%20other.%20%26quot%3BWe%20inform%20each%20other%2C%20there%20is%20no%20issue%20at%20all.%26quot%3B%20Grazing%2C%20which%20was%20required%20to%20be%20carried%20out%2C%20has%20been%20opened%20up.%20Whenever%20there%20i