go%20right%20down%20the%20line.%20India%20charges%20us%20massive%20tariffs%2C%20massive%2C%20you%20can't%20even%20sell%20anything%20into%20India.%20It's%20almost%2C%20it's%20almost%20restrictive.%20It%20is%20restrictive.%20We%20do%20very%20little%20business%20inside%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey've%20agreed%2C%20by%20the%20way%2C%20they%20want%20to%20cut%20their%20tariffs%20way%20down%20now%20because%20somebody's%20finally%20exposing%20them%20for%20what%20they've%20done.%20And%20the%20same%20thing%20with%20China%2C%20same%20thing%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20other%20countries%2C%20and%20the%20EU%20has%20been%20a%20terrible%20abuser%20of%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20to%20the%20comment%2C%20sources%20said%20India%20has%20reduced%20its%20average%20applied%20tariffs%20significantly%20for%20key%20developed%20countries%20like%20Australia%2C%20UAE%2C%20Switzerland%2C%20Norway%2C%20etc%20under%20the%20recently%20concluded%20mutually%20beneficial%20bilateral%20trade%20agreements.%20Similar%20negotiations%20are%20currently%20underway%20with%20the%20European%20Union%20and%20the%20United%20Kingdom%2C%20among%20other%20partners.%20The%20ongoing%20discussions%20with%20the%20United%20States%20should%20be%20seen%20in%20this%20context%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20India%20and%20the%20US%20in%20February%20agreed%20to%20negotiate%20the%20first%20tranche%20of%20a%20mutually%20beneficial%20multi-sector%20Bilateral%20Trade%20Agreement%20(BTA)%20by%20fall%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20President%20Trump%20agreed%20to%20designate%20senior%20representatives%20to%20advance%20the%20negotiations%2C%20and%20to%20work%20towards%20increasing%20market%20access%2C%20reducing%20tariff%20and%20non-tariff%20barriers%2C%20and%20deepening%20supply%20chain%20integration%2C%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccordingly%2C%20an%20Indian%20delegation%20led%20by%20Mr%20Goyal%20visited%20Washington%20DC%20from%203%20to%206%20March%20and%20met%20the%20US%20Commerce%20Secretary%2C%20the%20US%20Trade%20Representative%2C%20and%20their%20teams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20discussions%20on%20tariffs%20and%20other%20aspects%20of%20trade%20that%20were%20highlighted%20during%20PM%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20Washington%20DC%20are%20an%20ongoing%20process.%20Obviously%2C%20there%20are%20specifics%20which%20have%20been%20mentioned%20on%20various%20issues%20as%20part%20of%20the%20negotiation%2C%20they%20said%2C%20adding%20it%20is%20also%20natural%20that%20both%20countries%20have%20their%20interests%20and%20sensitivities.%20These%20are%20legitimate%20matters%20for%20a%20discussion%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20first%20Trump%20administration%2C%20discussions%20also%20took%20place%20about%20a%20limited%20trade%20deal%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20and%20for%20various%20reasons%2C%20it%20did%20not%20produce%20an%20outcome%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20discussions%20have%20just%20begun%2C%20it%20would%20be%20premature%20to%20talk%20about%20its%20details%2C%20they%20said.%20There%20is%20also%20a%20context%20for%20each%20dimension%20that%20would%20reflect%20the%20interests%20of%20both%20sides.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741443240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-11%2Fv26jovgg_container-ship-generic-istock_625x300_09_November_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fnegotiations-for-bilateral-trade-pact-underway-sources-amid-us-tariff-threat-7878747%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20said%20India%20has%20agreed%20to%20cut%20its%20tariffs%20%26quot%3Bway%20down%26quot%3B%20as%20he%20reiterated%20his%20claim%20that%20the%20country%20charges%20America%20massive%20tariffs%20that%20make%20it%20difficult%20to%20sell%20products%20there.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%2