ified%20as%20Bobby%2C%20Golu%2C%20Nitin%20Jain%2C%20and%20Jitu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20of%20the%20five%20arrested%20from%20Delhi%20are%20Manish%20Sahani%2C%20Yogesh%20Kukeja%2C%20and%20Suraj%2C%20all%20linked%20to%20Dubai.%20%C2%A0The%20police%20recovered%20Rs%2022%20lakh%20in%20cash%20from%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManish%20Sahani%20was%20the%20main%20operator%20of%20the%20gang.%20He%20would%20record%20voices%20of%20the%20people%20participating%20in%20betting%20and%20manage%20transactions%20through%20bank%20accounts%20or%20cash.%20He%20told%20police%20he%20did%20not%20involve%20any%20middleman%20and%20controlled%20the%20entire%20betting%20operation%20himself.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20interrogation%2C%20the%20three%20accused%20said%20Mannu%20Matka%2C%20Akshay%20Gehlot%2C%20Nishu%2C%20Rinku%2C%20and%20Aman%20Rajput%20developed%20the%20'Satta'%20betting%20app%20outside%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741440420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fp89gi18g_bookies_625x300_08_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frs-5-000-crore-bets-linked-to-underworld-placed-on-india-new-zealand-final-say-sources-7878364%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Bets%20worth%20up%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%20crore%20have%20been%20placed%20on%20the%20final%20match%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%20to%20be%20held%20in%20Dubai%20on%20Sunday%2C%20sources%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Beginnings%E2%80%99%20Review%3A%20Trine%20Dyrholm%20is%20Superb%20in%20an%20Emotionally%20Acute%20Portrait%20of%20a%20Divorce%20Disrupted%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741440315000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F03%2F202510027_1.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236331129%22%2C%22summ