required%20in%20Maharashtra%20%3A%20CM%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741436935000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-118805037%2Cimgsize-36008.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Flove-jihad-law-required-in-maharashtra-cm-devendra-fadnavis%2Farticleshow%2F118805046.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20emphasized%20the%20need%20for%20a%20'Love%20Jihad'%20law%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20referencing%20over%20a%20lakh%20complaints.%20He%20also%20spoke%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20daughters%2C%20women's%20independence%2C%20and%20the%20evolving%20role%20of%20women%20in%20politics%20during%20an%20International%20Women's%20Day%20event.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PRIYANKA%20KAKODKAR%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Flove-jihad-law-required-in-maharashtra-cm-devendra-fadnavis%2Farticleshow%2F118805046.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Will%20Punish%20Forced%20Conversion%20With%20Death%20In%20Madhya%20Pradesh'%3A%20Mohan%20Yadav%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIntensifying%20the%20BJP's%20attack%20on%20alleged%20instances%20of%20'love%20jihad'%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20Chief%20Minister%20Mohan%20Yadav%20has%20said%20his%20government%20will%20bring%20a%20law%20to%20ensure%20death%20penalty%20for%20those%20found%20guilty%20of%20forced%20religious%20conversions.%20Mr%20Yadav%20made%20the%20announcement%20at%20an%20event%20marking%20International%20Women's%20Day%2C%20asserting%20that%20forced%20conversions%20will%20not%20be%20allowed%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20government%20is%20very%20strict%20against%20those%20who%20commit%20atrocities%20against%20our%20innocent%20daughters.%20We%20won't%20spare%20those%20who%20force%20them.%20Such%20people%20should%20not%20be%20allowed%20to%20live.%20Through%20the%20Religious%20Freedom%20Act%2C%20we%20are%20working%20to%20extend%20the%20provision%20of%20death%20penalty%20to%20those%20doing%20forced%20conversions%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20strongly%20opposed%20the%20move.%20Congress%20MLA%20Arif%20Masood%20has%20accused%20the%20BJP%20government%20of%20targeting%20a%20particular%20religion%20and%20asked%20if%20it%20was%20attempting%20to%20alter%20the%20Constitution.%20%26quot%3BA%20girl%20has%20been%20missing%20in%20Bhopal%20for%20three%20days.%20We%20should%20find%20her.%20But%20targeting%20a%20particular%20community%20has%20always%20been%20their%20habit%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Masood%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmadhya-pradesh-government-notifies-law-against-religious-conversion-2402563%5C%22%3EReligious%20Freedom%20Act%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20passed%20by%20the%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20assembly%20on%20March%208%2C%202021%20with%20the%20BJP%20hardening%20its%20stance%20against%20forced%20conversions.%20The%20BJP%20often%20uses%20the%20term%20%26quot%3Blove%20jihad%26quot%3B%20to%20refer%20to%20an%20alleged%20conspiracy%20by%20Muslim%20men%20to%20lure%20Hindu%20women%20to%20marry%20them%20and%20convert%20to%20Islam.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fconversion-act-there-to-ensure-religious-freedom-for-all-says-allahabad-hc-rejects-mans-bail-6330534%5C%22%3EUttar%20Pradesh%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Gujarat%2C%20which%20have%20BJP%20governments%2C%20too%20have%20similar%20laws%20to%20curb%20such%20forced%20conversions%20while%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdevendra-fadnavis-bjp-shiv-sena-ncp-maharashtra-sets-up-7-member-panel-to-help-frame-law-against-love-jihad-7717778%5C%22%3EDevendra%20Fadnavis%20government%20in%20Maharashtra%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20set%20up%20a%20panel%20to%20study%20the%20aspects%20that%20can%20be%20included%20in%20a%20future%20legislation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20law%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20a%20provision%20to%20punish%20those%20found%20guilty%20of%20illegal%20conversion%20with%20up%20to%2010%20years%20imprisonment%20and%20a%20hefty%20fine.%20The%20law%20covers%20religious%20conversions%20through%20fraudulent%20means%2C%20like%20the%20pretext%20of%20marriage%2C%20misrepresentation%2C%20use%20of%20threat%20or%20force%2C%20influence%2C%20and%20coercion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20states%20that%20any%20marriage%20solemnised%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20law%20will%20be%20declared%20void.%20In%20cases%20of%20marriage%20by%20hiding%20religion%2C%20violators%20could%20also%20be%20punished%20with%20up%20to%2010%20years%20in%20jail%20and%20a%20fine%20of%20Rs%2050%2C000.%20The%20Act%20allows%20the%20converted%20person's%20parents%2C%20legal%20guardians%2C%20or%20siblings%20to%20lodge%20a%20complaint.%20Those%20willing%20to%20convert%20must%20apply%20to%20the%20district%20administration%2060%20days%20in%20advance%2C%20the%20law%20states.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20mark%20Women's%20Day%2C%20Mr%20Yadav%20today%20handed%20over%20the%20charge%20of%20his%20office%20in%20Bhopal%20to%20women.%20His%20security%20arrangements%20were%20also%20looked%20after%20by%20women%20police%20officers.%20His%20car%20was%20also%20driven%20by%20a%20woman%20driver.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20occasion%20of%20women's%20day%2C%20today%20all%20the%20responsibilities%20of%20my%20office%2C%20including%20driving%20to%20security%2C%20have%20been%20handed%20over%20to%20women.%20I%20have%20some%20women-centric%20programs%20to%20attend%20today.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20also%20running%20many%20schemes%20which%20will%20improve%20the%20lives%20of%20our%20sisters%20and%20will%20become%20an%20ideal%20example%20in%20women%20empowerment%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20said%20earlier%20in%20the%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741436760000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F20