-13324023%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20Struck%20On%20Knee%20Ahead%20Of%20CT%202025%20Final%2C%20Stops%20Training%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIndia%20are%20set%20to%20take%20on%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20final%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%20The%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20will%20aim%20to%20clinch%20its%20second%20ICC%20title%20in%20less%20than%20a%20year.%20In%20June%202024%2C%20India%20won%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20trophy.%20Talking%20about%20the%20ongoing%20tournament%2C%20Rohit%20and%20co.%20have%20looked%20in%20great%20touch.%20They%20won%20all%20their%20three%20group%20stage%20matches%2C%20playing%20against%20Bangladesh%2C%20Pakistan%20and%20New%20Zealand%2C%20before%20defeating%20Australia%20in%20the%20semi-final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20have%20got%20a%20big%20injury%20scare%20ahead%20of%20the%20summit%20clash%20as%20star%20batter%20Virat%20Kohli%20reportedly%20got%20hit%20on%20his%20knee%20during%20a%20practice%20session.%20Sharing%20the%20report%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.geo.tv%2Flatest%2F594277-virat-kohli-suffers-injury-during-practice-session-ahead-of-champions-trophy-final%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EGeo%20TV%3C%2Fa%3E%20explained%20that%20Kohli%20copped%20the%20blow%20after%20getting%20hit%20by%20a%20fast%20bowler's%20delivery.%20He%20quickly%20stopped%20the%20training%20and%20was%20attended%20by%20the%20physio%2C%20who%20applied%20a%20spray%20and%20wrapped%20the%20injured%20area%20with%20a%20bandage%2C%20it%20said.%20While%20Kohli%20didn't%20bat%20after%20that%2C%20the%20report%20added%20that%20the%20Indian%20coaching%20staff%20clarified%20that%20the%20injury%20is%20not%20serious%20and%20Kohli%20will%20play%20the%20final.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeldom%20does%20a%20Kohli%20knock%20in%20a%20winning%20chase%20leaves%20one%20wanting%20for%20more.%20But%20his%2084%20that%20guided%20India%20to%20a%20semifinal%20victory%20over%20Australia%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20in%20Dubai%20had%20that%20touch%20of%20incompleteness%20to%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20familiar%20Kohli%20hundred%20on%20Tuesday%20would%20have%20been%20his%2025th%20three-figure%20mark%20while%20hunting%20down%20a%20target.%20But%20the%20master%20would%20not%20be%20too%20displeased%20about%20the%20knock%20he%20eventually%20managed%20as%20he%20ticked%20many%20boxes.%20Here%20are%20the%20two%20most%20important%20of%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBox%20No.1%3A%20He%20tamed%20spinners%2C%20an%20Achilles%20Heel%20that%20haunted%20him%20for%20long%2C%20and%20more%20recently%20exploited%20by%20England's%20Adil%20Rashid%20and%20Bangladesh's%20Rishad%20Hossain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBox%20No.2%3A%20The%20fifty%20was%20full%20of%20determination%20to%20defeat%20an%20opponent%20who%20had%20given%20India%20and%20him%20several%20heartbreaks%20in%20the%20past.%20Through%20it%2C%20he%2C%20perhaps%2C%20was%20conveying%20his%20readiness%20to%20battle%20on%20for%20some%20more%20time%2C%20conquer%20some%20more%20peaks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%20has%20not%20come%20without%20its%20share%20of%20hard%20work.%20Kohli%20had%20to%20spend%20an%20extra%20two%20hours%20at%20nets%20to%20polish%20his%20skills%20ahead%20of%20the%20match%20against%20Pakistan%20after%20he%20was%20dismissed%20by%20Hossain%20against%20Bangladesh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubsequently%2C%20he%20negated%20Pakistan's%20Abrar%20Ahmed%2C%20but%20Adam%20Zampa%20is%20in%20a%20different%20league%20as%20a%20white%20ball%20leg-spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20slow%20Dubai%20pitch%20that%20slows%20down%20even%20more%20during%20the%20second%20half%20would%20have%20given%20more%20zing%20to%20Zampa's%20craft.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20their%20first%20meeting%20in%202017%2C%20Zampa%20had%20dismissed%20Kohli%20five%20times%20in%20white%20ball%20formats%2C%20and%20counterattack%20has%20been%20Kohli's%20preferred%20way%20to%20nullify%20the%20Aussie%20leg-spinner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%20match%2C%20Kohli%20had%20made%20264%20runs%20off%20245%20balls%20against%20him%20at%20a%20strike-rate%20of%20107.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20pitch%20here%20demanded%20a%20different%20approach%20from%20Kohli%20as%20he%20ticked%20off%20Zampa%2C%20taking%2023%20off%2024%20balls.%20He%20also%20made%2012%20runs%20off%20nine%20balls%20against%20Tanveer%20Sangha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20spectacular%20but%20effective%20in%20a%20tricky%20chase%20of%20265%2C%20even%20though%20he%20eventually%20fell%20to%20Zampa.%20But%20much%20after%20the%20team's%20job%20was%20done.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20will%20hope%20from%20Kohli%20to%20carry%20the%20same%20form%20in%20the%20final%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1741436640000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fv6em4th8_virat-kohli-afp_625x300_08_March_25.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fvirat-kohli-struck-on-knee-ahead-of-champions-trophy-2025-final-stops-training-report-7877852%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India%20are%20set%20to%20take%20on%20New%20Zealand%20in%20the%20final%20of%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20at%20the%20Dubai%20International%20Cricket%20Stadium%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-champions-trophy-2025%2Fvirat-kohli-struck-on-knee-ahead-of-champions-trophy-2025-final-stops-training-report-7877852%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Hamas%20Ready%20For%20Direct%20Talks%20With%20US%2C%20But%20Accuses%20Trump%20Of%20%26quot%3BDouble%20Standards%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20Hamas%20official%2C%20Mushir%20al-Masri%2C%20has%20accused%20Donald%20Trump%20of%20having%20%26quot%3Bblatant%20double%20standards%26quot%3B%20regarding%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%20in%20Gaza.%20Al-Masri's%20comments%20came%20after%20the%20White%20House%20confirmed%20direct%20negotiations%20with%20Hamas%20to%20secure%20the%20release%20of%20hostages%2C%20marking%20a%20significant%20shift%20in%20US%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20talks%20between%20Hamas%20and%20the%20US%20aim%20to%20achieve%20stability%20in%20the%20region%2C%20al-Masri%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fedition.cnn.com%2F2025%2F03%2F07%2Fmiddleeast%2Fhamas-reaction-us-talks-hostages-intl%2Findex.html%5C%22%3ECNN%3C%2Fa%3E.%20However%2C%20the%20Gaza%20ceasefire%20remains%20precarious%2C%20with%20Israel%20blocking%20vital%20aid%20to%20pressure%20Hamas%20into%20extending%20the%20truce.%20Israel%20has%20refused%20to%20engage%20in%20direct%20talks%20with%20Hamas%20since%20the%20October%207%20terror%20attack%20and%20has%20vowed%20to%20eliminate%20the%20group.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Masri%20emphasised%20that%20Hamas%20seeks%20to%20resolve%20the%20hostage%20issue%20in%20exchange%20for%20negotiations%20on%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20ceasefire.%20This%20would%20involve%20the%20release%20of%20remaining%20live%20hostages%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20sustainable%20end%20to%20the%20fighting.%20Currently%2C%20only%20one%20living%20American%20hostage%2C%20Edan%20Alexander%2C%20is%20believed%20to%20remain%20in%20Gaza%2C%20along%20with%20four%20dead%20Americans%20and%20at%20least%2012%20dual%20US-Israeli%20captives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAl-Masri%20criticised%20Trump%20for%20focussing%20on%20Israeli%20prisoners%20while%20ignoring%20the%20nearly%2010%2C000%20Palestinian%20detainees%20in%20Israeli%20prisons.%20He%20also%20accused%20the%20US%20administration%20of%20bias%20toward%20Israel%2C%20positioning%20itself%20as%20a%20party%20to%20the%20conflict%20rather%20than%20a%20mediator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20talks%2C%20Trump%20has%20continued%20to%20threaten%20Hamas%2C%20stating%20th