our%20life%2C%20you%20tend%20to%20meet%20leg%20pullers.%20I%20did%20not%20find%20support%20in%20people%20but%20in%20my%20plants%20themselves.%20Their%20growth%20kept%20my%20dignity%20alive.%20Sometimes%2C%20I%20feel%20communicating%20my%20desires%20to%20them%20is%20easier%20than%20expressing%20it%20to%20any%20human%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ENurturing%20a%20dream%20against%20all%20odds%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Garg%20had%20initiated%20the%20remarkable%20transformation%20without%20the%20luxury%20of%20fertile%20soil%2C%20ample%20water%2C%20or%20financial%20backing.%20He%20began%20with%20species%20like%20Banyan%2C%20Neem%2C%20Pipal%2C%20Mango%2C%20and%20Guava.%20Slowly%20but%20steadily%2C%20life%20began%20to%20sprout.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20he%20has%20planted%2040%2C000%20trees%20in%20the%20last%20eight%20years.%20Of%20these%2C%20about%2015%2C000%20trees%20have%20grown%20to%20heights%20above%2012%20feet.%20The%20survival%20rate%20of%20these%20trees%2C%20Dr%20Garg%20says%2C%20is%20an%20astounding%2095%20percent%20%E2%80%93%20a%20figure%20that%20silences%20his%20critics.%20His%20mission%20is%20to%20plant%2010%2C000%20more%20trees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20years%2C%20it%20has%20become%20a%20thriving%20ecosystem%20filled%20with%20teakwood%2C%20rosewood%2C%20sandalwood%2C%20and%20an%20astonishing%20variety%20of%20fruits%2C%20medicinal%2C%20and%20flowering%20trees%20from%20around%20the%20world%20%E2%80%93%20from%20Olives%20from%20Italy%20and%20Spain%2C%20Australian%20avocados%2C%20and%20Mexican%20dates%20have%20all%20found%20a%20home%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhat%20adds%20mystique%20to%20this%20endeavour%20is%20the%20trial%20and%20suc