0initial%20stages%20to%20cultivate%20this%20ecosystem%20were%20fraught%20with%20adversity.%20Dr%20Garg%20had%20drilled%20three%20borewells%20to%20arrange%20for%20a%20water%20source%20to%20water%20his%20saplings%2C%20but%20he%20found%20them%20all%20dry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUndeterred%2C%20he%20resorted%20to%20purchasing%20water%20through%20tankers%2C%20an%20exhaustive%20and%20expensive%20process.%20%E2%80%9CEach%20tanker%20of%206%2C000%20litres%20cost%20me%20about%20Rs%20600%20in%20normal%20days%20and%20Rs%202%2C000%20in%20summer.%20At%20least%20one%20water%20tanker%20was%20required%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20years%20later%2C%20the%20water%20table%20in%20surrounding%20areas%2C%20once%20considered%20hopeless%2C%20has%20risen%2C%20thanks%20to%20the%20forest%E2%80%99s%20influence%20on%20local%20water%20cycles.%20%E2%80%9CEarlier%2C%20I%20did%20not%20get%20water%20even%20after%20digging%20borewells%20as%20deep%20as%20600%20feet.%20Now%2C%20I%20get%20water%20in%20the%20surrounding%20plain%20areas%20at%20just%20250%20feet.%20Now%2C%20I%20am%20not%20dependent%20on%20water%20tankers%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20forest%20continues%20to%20mature%2C%20Dr%20Garg%20envisions%20its%20fragrant%20blossoms%20and%20vibrant%20foliage%20spreading%20joy%20and%20awareness%20far%20beyond%20the%20hill%20itself.%20His%20efforts%20extend%20an%20open%20invitation%20to%20anyone%20inspired%20to%20turn%20dreams%20into%20reality%2C%20even%20if%20it%20means%20being%20called%20%E2%80%98crazy%E2%80%99%20along%20the%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20readers%2C%20he%20has%20just%20one%20simple%20message%3A%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20should%20at%20least%20plant%20one%20tree%20in%20their%20lifetime.%20While%20you%20may%20think%20you%20are%20only%20planting%20a%20tree%2C%20it%20will%20give%20you%20and%20others%20fresh%20air%2C%20food%2C%20and%20shelter%2C%20boost%20the%20economy%2C%20and%20prevent%20disasters%20like%20floods%2C%20drought%20and%