20These%20sessions%20were%20incredibly%20valuable%2C%20teaching%20me%20how%20to%20navigate%20interviews%20and%20build%20my%20personality.%20Since%20I%20came%20from%20a%20Marathi%20medium%20background%2C%20English%20had%20always%20been%20a%20challenge%20for%20me.%20But%20through%20activities%20focused%20on%20personality%20building%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20English%20speaking%2C%20I%20slowly%20overcame%20my%20difficulties%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeyond%20soft%20skills%2C%20the%20initiative%20helped%20her%20learn%20coding%2C%20website%20development%2C%20and%20programming%20languages%20like%20C%2B%2B%20and%20Java%2C%20all%20of%20which%20supported%20her%20through%20her%20academic%20journey%20at%20MKSSS%E2%80%99s%20Cummins%20College%20of%20Engineering%2C%20Pune.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDuring%20my%20third%20year%2C%20when%20it%20was%20time%20for%20internships%2C%20I%20applied%20for%20an%20internship%20at%20Amazon.%20I%20attended%20the%20interview%2C%20and%20because%20of%20the%20confidence%20I%20gained%20through%20the%20sessions%2C%20I%20was%20able%20to%20perform%20well.%20I%20joined%20Amazon%20as%20a%20software%20engineer%20intern%20for%20two%20months%2C%20and%20by%20the%20end%20of%20my%20internship%2C%20I%20received%20a%20pre-placement%20offer.%20In%202023%2C%20I%20officially%20joined%20Amazon%20with%20a%20CTC%20of%20around%2046%20LPA%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20explains.%20Before%20joining%20Amazon%2C%20she%20worked%20as%20a%20mentor%2C%20taking%20technical%20sessions%20for%20beneficiaries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETurning%20dreams%20into%20careers%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20true%20impact%20of%20CybageKhushboo%20is%20reflected%20in%20the%20success%20of%20its%20students.%20In%20the%20early%20years%2C%20only%2025%25%20of%20graduates%20were%20able%20to%20secure%20jobs%2C%20highlighting%20the%20challenges%20they%20faced%20beyond%20academics.%20Recognising%20this%2C%20the%20team%20expanded%20its%20focus%20in%202014%E2